<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١٢٦٥ - <span class="c2">(ث ٣٥٥)</span> عن ابن عباس رضي الله عنهما<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>